"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640274737,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"2GjC359ZXIq_cGwV3s8fshZWyNBeNg77Vfv7La8k3oY\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x321c96b6B393ac40702D5e67CE2246fb805e3225\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"WbWg8ciinG8Izr-Sf3XQxQsWvAitNaXwl-HrdOg2oww\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"q1OpTu1kvhqQDDgCYDFSqBuPU3ZMNITaf9MMH_m4mI0\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"IUxJFinRG8zYSxhEirvMyHdrxi5pRvqe0GEAv-RdN6Ynb770H6iIHEMkd9Aj2rua4X-S0eVZbguwxuMkNgbFWA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x06abe85fc55f61b2e0c4374609b83da0002753252bc4eb516f51ec96a86a4bea4d8d65725bb785e9504ba239663cdb2f8c7f8a1e23585db5844d21f808cc8f961c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"WbWg8ciinG8Izr-Sf3XQxQsWvAitNaXwl-HrdOg2oww\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"q1OpTu1kvhqQDDgCYDFSqBuPU3ZMNITaf9MMH_m4mI0\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi